-1714107998.text: "Inhibition of MEK1 and MEK2 (activators of ERK1 and ERK2), PI3-kinase (activator of Akt) or Akt inhibited the axon growth promoting action of APRIL, as did pharmacological activation of GSK-3beta and the expression of a constitutively active form of GSK-3beta."
